{"tid":566832,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「有J圖」港女做韓星算唔算文化反擊第一步？","createTime":"2018-02-20T09:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T02:00:29.000Z","uid":40525,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b56a8c47c41a6d6a371ff96d103918e391468ecf","tid":566832,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"Elkie於2016年加入Cube娛樂旗下的女團CLC，因亮眼的外型而備受注目。曾有網民指Elkie的外表神似f(x)成員Krystal（鄭秀晶）。起初Elkie未有太多演唱機會，但於加入團體後的第二次回歸即演唱歌曲〈No oh oh〉的副歌部份，大騷出色唱功，不少網民都表示十分驚訝。其後她便有更多曝光機會，站在團隊的中心位置、發表個人翻唱作品等等，而最近Elkie更成為首位出演韓國電視劇的香港人，參與MBC電視台的新週末劇《富家之子》，在劇中飾演到韓國留學的中國人。童星出身，有豐富拍劇經驗的Elkie，演出令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n不過其他女醜樣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sKzkuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sKzkuU&d=RWi8%2FMXaRyFL6ul%2B8aR%2FuTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a6e43d9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sKzkuU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/173524_c6f7c6014e8aa2bcc679d4d0501956de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F173524_c6f7c6014e8aa2bcc679d4d0501956de.jpg&h=3a2d811d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/173525_bdf0bee359c3b831fe64448e2b500e73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F173525_bdf0bee359c3b831fe64448e2b500e73.jpg&h=f6a24163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/173525_1b97e884e0cf6a5eaf6dec23023a6c12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F173525_1b97e884e0cf6a5eaf6dec23023a6c12.jpg&h=9df3753e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/173526_07d41a545e35b7bb704fb6b19c63c1ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht